00:01:27.456 --> 00:01:30.893
=The Maid=

00:01:31.425 --> 00:01:34.381
=Episode 12=

00:01:34.496 --> 00:01:35.560
(Dali Court)

00:01:35.560 --> 00:01:36.440
I want to

00:01:36.440 --> 00:01:38.520
appeal for justice
for my sworn sister Lin Jifu.

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:40.480
In the Prince Regent's Mansion,

00:01:40.480 --> 00:01:42.080
there are those
with the nature of wolves

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:43.640
and the hearts of vipers,

00:01:43.640 --> 00:01:44.680
plotting against lives.

00:01:45.080 --> 00:01:46.840
I beg Your Honor to uncover the truth

00:01:47.280 --> 00:01:48.280
to console the departed

00:01:48.280 --> 00:01:49.360
and ease their spirits.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:54.240
I beg Your Honor

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:56.440
to investigate the death of Lin Jifu

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:57.760
from the Duke's Mansion.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.160
What's going on?

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:01.280
Prince Regent's concubine

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:03.160
came to us instead
of seeking the Prince Regent.

00:02:03.160 --> 00:02:05.360
She must be accusing someone
the Prince Regent protects.

00:02:05.984 --> 00:02:06.824
The Princess Consort?

00:02:07.240 --> 00:02:08.640
My lord, how should we handle this?

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:10.640
We can't afford to offend either party.

00:02:13.440 --> 00:02:14.560
A life hangs in balance.

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:15.720
If you refuse this case,

00:02:16.200 --> 00:02:17.240
I won't leave.

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.440
Let the people see

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:20.960
how the Dali Court

00:02:21.080 --> 00:02:22.560
abandons justice.

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:27.520
I

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:29.160
will accompany you to the mansion.

00:02:30.720 --> 00:02:31.920
Thank you, My lord.

00:02:32.960 --> 00:02:35.072
(Hold on, Xiyu.)

00:02:35.072 --> 00:02:37.120
(I'll rescue you
from this den of demons.)

00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:40.352
(Testimony)

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:51.160
Stop!

00:02:54.760 --> 00:02:55.920
You dare show your face?

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:00.240
Xiyu.

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:05.600
I'm sorry.

00:03:06.160 --> 00:03:07.680
I came too late.

00:03:08.800 --> 00:03:10.200
I didn't sign.

00:03:10.760 --> 00:03:12.160
I didn't sign it.

00:03:12.192 --> 00:03:13.920
(Testimony)

00:03:17.760 --> 00:03:18.680
I know.

00:03:19.200 --> 00:03:20.120
I know.

00:03:21.280 --> 00:03:22.960
(Shen Yuqing.)

00:03:23.120 --> 00:03:24.800
(Let's see you keep pretending.)

00:03:28.160 --> 00:03:29.680
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:03:30.040 --> 00:03:31.680
Greetings, My lady.

00:03:33.640 --> 00:03:35.712
You'd better not meddle

00:03:35.712 --> 00:03:36.720
in the Prince Regent's

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:38.240
inner household matters.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.200
My lord,

00:03:42.600 --> 00:03:44.200
the Princess Consort murdered Lin Jifu

00:03:44.440 --> 00:03:46.400
and tortured maid Xiyu

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:49.040
to silence witnesses.

00:03:50.080 --> 00:03:51.600
More nonsense,

00:03:52.040 --> 00:03:53.360
and I'll tear up your mouth!

00:03:53.360 --> 00:03:55.040
Who's stirring up

00:03:55.080 --> 00:03:57.160
this settled case?

00:04:00.880 --> 00:04:02.520
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:10.800
Now,

00:04:10.800 --> 00:04:11.800
go to the suburban camp

00:04:11.800 --> 00:04:13.360
and inform the Prince Regent.

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:15.080
Urge him to intervene.

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:15.920
Yes, My lord.

00:04:16.200 --> 00:04:17.760
(Pei Ji, since you won't act,)

00:04:17.760 --> 00:04:19.480
(I'll have to make this effort)

00:04:19.920 --> 00:04:22.000
(to have your subordinates summon you.)

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:27.280
Your Highness,

00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:29.360
why have you returned?

00:04:31.960 --> 00:04:32.960
Your mother claims

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:34.120
the Lin Jifu matter

00:04:34.120 --> 00:04:35.040
is already resolved.

00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:38.200
With Fu's sudden passing,

00:04:38.360 --> 00:04:40.080
the maid who once cared for her

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:41.920
cannot escape blame.

00:04:42.880 --> 00:04:44.560
I will investigate thoroughly.

00:04:49.920 --> 00:04:51.040
The Duchess

00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:53.480
is feigning one aim
while plotting another.

00:04:54.080 --> 00:04:55.000
My humble self

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.160
matters not,

00:04:56.358 --> 00:04:57.960
but your duplicity
toward His Highness...

00:04:57.960 --> 00:04:59.560
When I speak to His Highness,

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:01.720
a concubine like you
shouldn't interrupt.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:06.240
If you wish to investigate,

00:05:06.840 --> 00:05:07.840
let it be done.

00:05:08.840 --> 00:05:09.680
I remember

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:11.720
the last to see Lin Jifu

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:14.160
was the Princess Consort, right?

00:05:21.520 --> 00:05:22.760
What do you imply?

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:25.320
Whoever persists

00:05:25.320 --> 00:05:26.320
in this matter

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:27.840
or stirs discord

00:05:28.040 --> 00:05:29.560
will face severe punishment.

00:05:36.600 --> 00:05:37.440
Take her away.

00:05:41.640 --> 00:05:42.240
Go.

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:43.760
Xiyu, let's go.

00:05:55.488 --> 00:05:58.179
(Testimony)

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:06.040
That cunning maid

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:07.520
should not be underestimated.

00:06:16.560 --> 00:06:17.680
Shen Yuqing.

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.520
Daughter of the Duke's concubine.

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:31.880
Three years ago,

00:06:31.920 --> 00:06:33.600
disappeared with Qin Xiaoniang.

00:06:35.400 --> 00:06:37.440
Coincidentally that same year,

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:41.080
Meixiang House gained a courtesan
named Xiyan.

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:45.000
Ye Xiyan,

00:06:46.280 --> 00:06:48.000
you are Shen Yuqing.

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.040
Yes.

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:03.240
You admit it.

00:07:04.280 --> 00:07:06.280
Even with a hundred reasons to refuse,

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:08.520
as long as it pleases you,

00:07:09.120 --> 00:07:11.440
I would willingly serve
as Shen Yuqing's substitute.

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.600
If you're not Shen Yuqing,

00:07:15.600 --> 00:07:17.240
why would Xiyu betray her mistress?

00:07:17.240 --> 00:07:19.760
And why go through such lengths
to save a maid?

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:23.400
Xiyu suffered Lin Jifu's oppression
for years,

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:25.200
living in constant peril.

00:07:25.800 --> 00:07:27.120
Death will come either way.

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:28.880
Why not risk everything?

00:07:29.640 --> 00:07:31.080
You hold such a high position.

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:32.280
How could you understand us,

00:07:32.280 --> 00:07:34.240
mere mortals as small as ants?

00:07:35.280 --> 00:07:37.080
If we want to survive,

00:07:37.200 --> 00:07:39.600
we have to rise from the ashes
of our demise.

00:07:42.640 --> 00:07:43.760
You're not me.

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:46.200
How can you presume I don't understand?

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:48.160
If you understand,

00:07:49.320 --> 00:07:51.400
why abandon me to my fate?

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:53.520
They tortured Xiyu, forcing her

00:07:53.680 --> 00:07:55.760
to testify I'm the daughter
of the Duke's concubine.

00:07:56.320 --> 00:07:56.960
Then,

00:07:57.280 --> 00:07:59.240
they'd drag me back
to the Duke's Mansion,

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:01.520
leaving me with no escape but death.

00:08:04.040 --> 00:08:05.000
By this logic,

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:07.240
the fault lies with me?

00:08:07.360 --> 00:08:08.440
What fault could you have?

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:10.840
All faults belong to me.

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:15.160
I erred

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:17.680
by knowing I'm merely your blade,

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:20.080
yet failing to remain

00:08:20.880 --> 00:08:22.600
an emotionless weapon.

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:40.360
Why have Xiyu

00:08:41.280 --> 00:08:42.360
taken away?

00:08:45.160 --> 00:08:46.120
Sell her off

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:47.840
as far from the capital as possible.

00:08:51.840 --> 00:08:53.080
I believe

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:55.440
you should keep her instead.

00:08:56.720 --> 00:08:59.160
Xiyu knows Lin Jifu's secrets.

00:08:59.320 --> 00:09:01.000
She could testify when needed.

00:09:01.800 --> 00:09:02.640
Such

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.640
leverage against the Duke's Mansion

00:09:05.160 --> 00:09:06.800
shouldn't be discarded.

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:12.800
I

00:09:12.960 --> 00:09:14.320
need no mere maid's confinement

00:09:14.800 --> 00:09:16.400
to confront the Duke's Mansion.

00:09:18.560 --> 00:09:20.240
You hold a high position,

00:09:20.390 --> 00:09:21.760
and steeped in state affairs.

00:09:22.480 --> 00:09:24.080
You're too occupied for such trifles.

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:26.120
Let me handle them instead.

00:09:27.520 --> 00:09:29.120
Since Madam Su and the Princess Consort

00:09:29.120 --> 00:09:31.040
already see me as their thorn,

00:09:32.280 --> 00:09:33.600
I'll gladly

00:09:34.040 --> 00:09:35.680
shoulder more burdens for you.

00:09:50.920 --> 00:09:51.920
In your hands,

00:09:53.000 --> 00:09:54.960
you'd make me worry more.

00:09:55.680 --> 00:09:56.840
In my hands

00:09:58.240 --> 00:10:00.040
means being in yours, doesn't it?

00:10:06.880 --> 00:10:08.120
You share the same purpose?

00:10:11.490 --> 00:10:13.000
The Princess Consort has her father,

00:10:13.640 --> 00:10:14.440
mother,

00:10:15.040 --> 00:10:16.160
and aunt.

00:10:17.680 --> 00:10:18.320
But I

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.880
stand utterly alone,

00:10:21.760 --> 00:10:22.720
you are my only one.

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:31.800
Your Highness.

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:45.600
One day,

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:49.840
I'll make your heart yearn for me.

00:11:17.840 --> 00:11:18.800
My lady.

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:19.960
Come in.

00:11:26.760 --> 00:11:28.040
My lady,

00:11:28.040 --> 00:11:29.400
all preparations are complete.

00:11:30.560 --> 00:11:31.440
Good.

00:11:32.120 --> 00:11:33.760
She's crafted clever schemes,

00:11:34.320 --> 00:11:36.080
and I've built countermeasures.

00:11:37.040 --> 00:11:39.160
Since I failed to condemn her with Xiyu,

00:11:39.560 --> 00:11:41.560
I'll take the drastic measure

00:11:41.720 --> 00:11:43.880
and lure her into our trap.

00:11:55.320 --> 00:11:57.120
I failed you.

00:12:00.480 --> 00:12:01.680
You arranged

00:12:03.040 --> 00:12:04.960
everything for me,

00:12:05.280 --> 00:12:06.560
yet I proved useless,

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:09.480
nearly dragging you down.

00:12:24.736 --> 00:12:26.560
(To Ye Xiyan)

00:12:48.896 --> 00:12:50.528
(Tomorrow at one quarter
past Shen hour,)

00:12:50.528 --> 00:12:51.440
(if you don't come,)

00:12:51.440 --> 00:12:54.640
(every corpse in the mass graves
outside the capital will be desecrated!)

00:12:54.760 --> 00:12:56.800
Madam Su is threatening me
with my mother's remains

00:12:57.320 --> 00:12:58.160
hostage?

00:13:01.200 --> 00:13:02.480
If you go tomorrow,

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:04.600
you admit being Shen Yuqing.

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:22.760
My lady,

00:13:23.400 --> 00:13:26.120
I've notified the Capital Prefect

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:28.240
that tomorrow we catch bandits
in west suburbs.

00:13:28.560 --> 00:13:29.280
We'll claim

00:13:29.280 --> 00:13:31.040
Shen Yuqing encountered our operation

00:13:31.640 --> 00:13:32.320
and got killed

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:34.480
by the bandits out of vengeance.

00:13:36.920 --> 00:13:39.040
After being the Chief Constable
of Capital Prefecture,

00:13:39.040 --> 00:13:40.840
your planning has become
much more thorough.

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:44.120
With this arrangement,

00:13:44.120 --> 00:13:46.320
if Pei Ji truly inquires about her fate,

00:13:46.560 --> 00:13:49.280
you can capture a few petty thieves
as scapegoats.

00:13:50.280 --> 00:13:52.920
The Duke's Mansion
will remain blameless.

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:54.760
My lady, you flatter me.

00:14:08.680 --> 00:14:09.760
Here's your payment.

00:14:21.600 --> 00:14:22.440
Thank you, My lady.

00:14:24.360 --> 00:14:25.840
You think it is insufficient?

00:14:27.640 --> 00:14:28.440
I wouldn't dare.

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:29.800
Wouldn't dare?

00:14:29.840 --> 00:14:32.120
Then you must have such thoughts.

00:14:37.400 --> 00:14:38.280
I deserve to die.

00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:40.280
Three years ago,

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:41.400
it was because of you

00:14:41.400 --> 00:14:43.080
that this catastrophe occurred today.

00:14:44.120 --> 00:14:45.160
I deserve to die.

00:14:45.760 --> 00:14:46.880
I deserve to die.

00:14:47.600 --> 00:14:48.600
I deserve to die.

00:14:48.960 --> 00:14:50.200
I deserve to die.

00:14:50.680 --> 00:14:51.760
I deserve to die.

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.200
I deserve to die.

00:14:54.120 --> 00:14:55.040
I deserve to die.

00:14:55.920 --> 00:14:57.320
I deserve to die.

00:14:57.520 --> 00:14:58.320
Enough.

00:15:03.640 --> 00:15:04.440
Thank you, My lady.

00:15:18.400 --> 00:15:19.880
Were it not for me,

00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:22.040
a mere thief like you

00:15:22.240 --> 00:15:24.760
could never become a Chief Constable.

00:15:26.680 --> 00:15:28.760
A bird with hardened wings

00:15:28.760 --> 00:15:30.240
may possess great skills,

00:15:30.880 --> 00:15:33.520
but its desires grow larger too.

00:15:54.200 --> 00:15:54.920
Boss.

00:15:56.880 --> 00:15:58.680
Why would there be a wedding sedan here?

00:15:59.760 --> 00:16:01.200
It can't be ghosts, right?

00:16:05.720 --> 00:16:07.480
Ghosts don't exist in this world.

00:16:07.880 --> 00:16:09.120
Even if they do,

00:16:09.560 --> 00:16:11.160
it's humans playing tricks.

00:16:11.640 --> 00:16:12.280
Follow me.

00:16:21.840 --> 00:16:22.840
As expected.

00:16:26.560 --> 00:16:28.560
How should I address you?

00:16:29.520 --> 00:16:30.720
Should I call you

00:16:31.080 --> 00:16:32.320
Lady Ye,

00:16:32.480 --> 00:16:34.360
or Shen Yuqing?

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:41.640
After her!

